    "client_msg_id": "42cc370e-bf3b-4964-ad89-278c0547060a",
    "text": "it means the idiomatic language debugger works (i.e. devtools), in contrast to shipping a facsimile which often happens with new coding environment.\n\nI would go slightly further and say the debugging experience is better than in normal Javascript because when code is updated to place a \"debugger expression\" it hot-reloads so then it immediately has the opportunity to catch an execution. debuggers + live coding have excellent synergy",
    "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "thread_ts": "1735565958.937269",
    "parent_user_id": "U02E4DAQGSZ",
    "blocks": [
